data.description:
Actual Address; 3522 Zephyr Glen Way Houston, TX 77084. Easy approval. Credit needs to be 620 or higher. No eviction, No broken lease, No dangerous or recent felony, good rent history. Monthly income must be at least 3x the rent.

Tenant is responsible for all utilities. Application fee $50.00 per adult 18 and up. First month's rent due at signing. No smoking allowed. Maximum 2 pets
